feedback.feedback: Amazing experience at Best Friends! The staff is incredibly knowledgeable and supportive. The facilities are top-notch and the animals are clearly well-cared for. I've been volunteering here for 2 years and it's been life-changing.

Great organization doing important work. The dog walking program is well-organized and the dogs are wonderful. Staff could be a bit more responsive to volunteer questions, but overall a positive experience.

Nuzzles & Co is doing incredible work with cat socialization. The volunteers are passionate and the cats receive excellent care. The facility could use some updates but the heart of this organization is amazing.

The work is important but the organization could be better managed. Training was minimal and I often felt unsure about procedures. The facility is adequate but could use improvements. Staff seems overwhelmed.
Love helping with their fundraising events! The team is super supportive and welcoming. Events are well-planned and successful. The main facility is a bit cramped but they make the most of it.

Excellent transport program! Very well organized with clear communication. I've helped transport over 50 dogs to their forever homes. The coordination team is fantastic and always available for questions.
Great administrative volunteer experience. The office work is meaningful and helps the rescue run smoothly. Staff is professional and appreciative of volunteer help. Good training provided.
Best Friends is truly the gold standard for animal rescue. The dog walking program is exceptional - well-trained staff, beautiful trails, and happy dogs. Every volunteer feels valued and supported.
Solid organization with good facilities. The animal care program is comprehensive but could use more volunteer support staff. Sometimes felt like I was thrown into situations without enough guidance.

The rescue does good work but needs better organization. Cleaning schedules were often unclear and supplies weren't always available. The animals are well-cared for but volunteer coordination could improve.
Wonderful cat program in Logan! The cats are well-socialized and the staff genuinely cares. Facility is older but clean. Great volunteer orientation and ongoing support.
Amazing transport rescue! They save dogs from high-kill shelters and transport them to loving homes. Very well organized with excellent communication. Proud to be part of this mission.
Great events team! Their adoption events are well-organized and successful. Beautiful facility in Murray. Staff is professional and volunteers are made to feel welcome and appreciated.
Incredible work with special needs animals. The staff's dedication is inspiring and they provide excellent training for volunteers. Facilities are adequate for their specialized needs.
